title: Dell 17R 5720 Windows 8 x64 Recovery Disks
description:
This is the full recovery disk set for Dell 17R 5720. These disks will fully restore all software originally installed on this model. This is Windows 8 x64. This will recreate all factory partitions as they were, including the recovery partition.

These are the recovery disks created when you first get the computer and contain no updates. 

There are different variations of these recovery disks and this may not contain all drivers or software shipped with your particular model. Your laptop should have came from the factory with Windows 8 for this to activate properly.

This should also work on similar models.

Disk 1 MD5; E7EAE624E7D1FD5A3ACFF2B8F9029F7A

Disk 2 MD5; 70CE53BD9E1C6084CE8D060F81045ED5

PLEASE SEED UNTIL AT LEAST 1:1 RATIO TO KEEP THIS TORRENT ALIVE FOR A LONG TIME TO COME.
